---
interface Props {}
---

<section class="py-10 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-12">
            こんなトラブル、お任せください
        </h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center group">
                <div class="aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 border border-gray-100 group-hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">
                    <span class="text-4xl">🤮</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm md:text-base">嘔吐・お漏らし</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">除菌・消臭まで徹底</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center group">
                <div class="aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 border border-gray-100 group-hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">
                    <span class="text-4xl">🚬</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm md:text-base">タバコ・ヤニ汚れ</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">天井まで丸ごと洗浄</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center group">
                <div class="aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 border border-gray-100 group-hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">
                    <span class="text-4xl">🛢️</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm md:text-base">灯油こぼし</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">強烈な臭いも分解</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center group">
                <div class="aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 border border-gray-100 group-hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">
                    <span class="text-4xl">🐾</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm md:text-base">ペットの粗相・毛</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">奥の毛まで強力吸引</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
